{"tid":1241433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上過前線既義士 小弟有個卑微既請求","createTime":"2019-06-18T16:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T06:44:42.000Z","uid":170772,"like":161,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"ea9a0a18ff117434a20d9d38c3232e2eb2bbfd9d","tid":1241433,"uid":170772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:50:35.000Z","msg":"發夢雨傘期間係旺角接觸過唔少勇武派既義士<br />\n我明白 你地當年被割席 被篤灰 甚至被同路人指責<br />\n我都明白 你地當中唔少人被捕入獄 即使沒有坐監 <br />\n都被多年來既官司纏身 精神打壓 已經心灰意冷<br />\n<br />\n但我仍然堅信你地係愛香港 唔想睇住我地死<br />\n係我地當年辜負左你地 希望你地不計前嫌 再次企出黎<br />\n帶領我地前線既義士！<br />\n<br />\n咁多年社運小弟都有發夢參與當中<br />\n始終冇一批人好似你地咁有系統性 咁有戰略<br />\n而且係團結一致 無畏無懼 進退合宜<br />\n<br />\n我唸大家612都有眼所見 我地係不乏前線人員<br />\n但大多都有勇無謀 而當中更多既係00後 我好欣賞佢哋<br />\n佢哋份勇氣唔低於我地當年 但可惜係佢哋當年冇參與到雨傘<br />\n欠缺經驗 一衝即散<br />\n<br />\n因此 懇求更多有經驗既前線義士企出黎<br />\n就算唔企前排 都可以帶領我地 提供意見 現場組織<br />\n將會事半功倍 更重要係減少被捕 受傷既義士<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1db87283953d0aa40578fcce397b20c94d9331","tid":1241433,"uid":156107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:51:30.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48a37a2d14b33e484a1775fd8a37f2ed4f42af7","tid":1241433,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec73889593f31f56426902f9c64417b30cd6f52","tid":1241433,"uid":170772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:52:21.000Z","msg":"621 我地需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0d3d2166837d751d5f8f420fcd5b13194a59dd","tid":1241433,"uid":170772,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:53:41.000Z","msg":"我唯一可以保證既係<br />\n今非昔比 我地比以往更團結<br />\n亦唔會再有人篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fa44fb3817a3fd4692883ede9b1192f11f28e7","tid":1241433,"uid":153144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5c2c63d232ba1465f1009ed6dc8bd37be12ae29a","tid":1241433,"uid":170772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:56:28.000Z","msg":"釐清<br />\n唔係想大家企出黎做出更大既反擊<br />\n只係想義士們提供經驗同策略<br />\n增強我地既防守力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8e10a36610827769027dcea3d656a32b280049","tid":1241433,"uid":170772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b0924eda4909308509d1d4c2d2e02f722124d1","tid":1241433,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"好多都係80後<br />\n包括就義既烈士<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51b7cc2a4b283ea2342daa26da481c263568916","tid":1241433,"uid":170772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:02:04.000Z","msg":"612就到<br />\n但連登仍然冇相關討論<br />\n冇提供任何策略 實在令人擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c6031290b83bbf6ab72a9ca4ea522f0731b2cf","tid":1241433,"uid":170772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:02:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b79c83ff4cf85b9da001fe84790af9349005036","tid":1241433,"uid":131259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:05:44.000Z","msg":"有不同意見係好正常既情況<br />\n勇武同和理非都互相體諒下<br />\n意見不合就傾多啲 唔好亂扣帽子"},{"pid":"3804c1868612e6bfe1b4006e5f35f784e8185b36","tid":1241433,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as